1. *Brani* me od napada psa. (Defend me from the dog's attack.)
2. Ona *brani* svoju diplomu sledeće nedelje. (She is defending her thesis next week.)
3. Advokat će *braniti* optuženog na suđenju. (The lawyer will defend the accused at the trial.)
4. Vojska je uspela da *odbrani* grad od neprijateljske invazije. (The army managed to defend the city from the enemy invasion.)
5. Treba da *branimo* naša prava i interese. (We need to defend our rights and interests.)
6. Ovaj zid *brani* od buke i zagađenja. (This wall shields us from noise and pollution.)
7. Oni *brane* da su oni u pravu. (They argue that they are right.)
8. Golman je uspešno *odbranio* gol od protivničkog napada. (The goalkeeper successfully defended the goal from the opponent's attack.)
9. Njegov postupak ne *brani* nikakvo opravdanje. (His behavior does not justify anything.)
10. Ova maska *brani* od virusa i bakterija. (This mask protects from viruses and bacteria.)